<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἀκύλας Σαραπίωνι 

    <lb n="2"/>χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>κομισάμενός σου τὰ γράμ-

    <lb n="4"/>ματα πάνυ ἥσθην. ᾗ μάλιστα 

    <lb n="5"/>ὁ ἡμέτερος Καλλίνεικος ἐμαρ-

    <lb n="6"/>τύρει περὶ τῆς διαίτης σου ἧς 

    <lb n="7"/>ποιῇ καὶ ἐν τοιούτοις ὢν 

    <lb n="8"/>πράγμασι<del rend="erasure">ν</del>, μάλιστα μὴ 

    <lb n="9"/>ἀφιστάμενος τῆς ἀσκήσεως. 

    <lb n="10"/>ἄξιον οὖν ἐστιν ἐπαινεῖν ἑ-

    <lb n="11"/>αυτούς, οὐχ ὅτι ποιοῦμεν ταῦ-

    <lb n="12"/>τα ἀλλὰ ὅτι μὴ ἐξαγόμεθα 

    <lb n="13"/>ὑφ᾽ ἑαυτ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῶν</supplied>· ἀνδραγάθ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied> οὖν 

    <lb n="14"/>καὶ τὰ λοιπὰ ἐπιτέλεσον 

    <lb n="15"/>ὡς ἀνὴ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρ ἀ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">γα</unclear>θός, καὶ μ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ή σ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear> 

    <lb n="16"/>ταρασσέ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ω</unclear> ἢ πλοῦτος ἢ ὥρα 

    <lb n="17"/>ἢ ἄλλο τ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι τ</supplied>ῶν <choice><corr>τοιούτων</corr><sic>τοιου<del rend="erasure">ν</del>των</sic></choice>, ὡς 

    <lb n="18"/>οὐδὲν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὄφ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ελ</supplied>ός ἐστιν ἀρετῆς 

    <lb n="19"/>μὴ παρούσης, ἀλλὰ φροῦδα καὶ οὐ-

    <lb n="20"/>δενὸς ἄξια. θεῶν σωζόντων 

    <lb n="21"/>προσδέχομαί σε ἐν τῇ Ἀντινόου. 

    <lb n="22"/>τὸ σκυλάκιον πέμψον Σωτη-

    <lb n="23"/>ρίδι, ἐπεὶ αὐτὴ νῦν ἐν ἀγρῷ <choice><corr>δια-

    <lb n="24"/>τριβει</corr><sic>διατρειβει</sic></choice>. <choice><corr>ἔρρωσο</corr><sic>ερρωσσο</sic></choice> σὺν τοῖς σοῖς. 

    <lb n="25"/><choice><corr>ἔρρωσο</corr><sic>ερρωσσο</sic></choice>. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="26"/>Σαραπίωνι   φιλοσόφωι 

    <lb n="27"/>παρὰ Ἀκύ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λου</unclear> 

    <lb n="28"/>φίλου. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.30336" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.30336" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="400" notBefore="201" type="textDate">III - IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.30336" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zum Ort vgl. Z. 21.</p></div><div n="meta.30336" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">42</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">3069</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">30336</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">42</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">3069</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;42;3069" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.30336" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.30336" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">Tibiletti, Lettere private 20</bibl></div><div n="meta.30336" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="en"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Trapp, Letters (2003), Nr. 35 (mit Text).</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="fr"><head lang="de">Französisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Burnet, L'Égypte ancienne (2003), Nr. 214.</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="it"><head lang="de">Italienisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Tibiletti, Lettere private (1979), 20</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.30336" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Antinoopolis</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.30336" part="N" type